Code preview of 资金流水表sl_fund_qlide

drop table if exists sl_fund_qlide;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: sl_fund_qlide */
/*==============================================================*/
create table sl_fund_qlide
(
fundQlideId bigint(20) not null auto_increment,
glideNum bigint(20) not null comment '资金流水号',
dialAccounts varchar(50) comment '拨款帐号',
dialMoney numeric(10,2) not null comment '拨款金额',
afterMoney numeric(10,2) comment '已对帐金额',
notMoney numeric(10,2) comment '未对帐金额',
factDate datetime not null comment '到帐日期',
recAccounts varchar(50) not null comment '收款帐号',
primary key (fundQlideId)
);

alter table sl_fund_qlide comment '资金流水表';
